docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, Nov. 1 (UPI) A court of honor ruled tonight that there were no legitimate reasons for a duel between President Oscar Gestido and Amilcar Vasconcellos, a member of the Uruguayan Senate. The men had agreed in advance to accept the ruling.

docs.snippet: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, Nov. 4 (UPI)--Racing of Buenos Aires won the World Cup soccer championship today with a 1-0 victory over the Glasgow Celtics before 75,000 fans. Five players were expelled from the game, which was marked by numerous fouls.
